(4020, 1, '2020-04-20 19:34:20', '2020-04-20 19:34:20', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph -->Due to the current COVID-19 restrictions, IPS is not able to offer onsite tours or Open House.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- wp:quote -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\r\n<p>The IPS Admissions Director will be available via call for prospective parents who are interested in learning more about the excellent programs offered at IPS for Toddlers (1-2 yrs), Children\'s House (pre-school), Elementary School.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph -->The Admissions Process</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- wp:quote -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\r\n<p>The Admissions process for The Ideal Public School is intended to offer families specific information about our school, as well as general information regarding IPS philosophy.</p>\r\n<p>The first step in our process is to download &amp; fill the admission form from the link. <a href=\"http://ipsdhayari.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ADMISSION-FROM-23.pdf\">ADMISSION FROM 23</a></p>\r\n<p>The next step is to scan &amp; send its soft copy to <a href=\"mailto:admin@ipsdhayari.co.in\">admin@ipsdhayari.co.in</a> or on Whatsapp number +91 9923905230</p>\r\n<p>Or call us at 8698035454/8087598790</p>\r\n<p>Our management team will process the submitted form &amp; will get back to you for next round.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>', 'Admissions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'admissions', '', '', '2020-04-20 20:59:04', '2020-04-20 20:59:04', '', 0, 'http://ipsdhayari.co.in/?page_id=4020', 0, 'page', '', 0),
